{"tid":534861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒黃浩銘申保釋","createTime":"2018-01-20T09:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T11:44:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc533f59590a960f3852a4c90a4c155216f2a14","tid":534861,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:07:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180120/20280137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F20280137&d=VATVdNANZ2xGWoSs%2F9z2db%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=550841a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F20280137&h=e6b553c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180120/20280137</a><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒黃浩銘申保釋<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n       <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180120/large/20la5p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180120%2Flarge%2F20la5p7.jpg&h=ad7535ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n【佔旺藐視法庭案】<br />\n【本報訊】2014年佔旺清場，黃之鋒（圖）、黃浩銘及岑敖暉等16人因未有依照禁制令離開，被控刑事藐視法庭罪。法官陳慶偉日前判黃之鋒、黃浩銘兩人分別入獄3個月及4個半月，並拒絕兩人的暫緩執行判決申請，須即時服刑。兩人昨向上訴庭入紙申請保釋，法庭排期下周二進行保釋申請聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下周二聆訊<br />\n<br />\n據司法機構網頁顯示，保釋申請聆訊定於下周二下午2時半在高院進行，由首席法官張舉能和上訴庭副庭長林文瀚負責審理，預計聆訊約一小時。黃之鋒及黃浩銘的大狀擔心兩人服刑完畢後仍未能排期上訴，日前向法官陳慶偉申請暫緩執行刑期，惟最終被拒。<br />\n<br />\n陳官日前在判詞指，黃之鋒扮演領導者角色，雖然他逗留現場只有個半小時，但其間不斷質疑禁制令申請人潮聯小巴的代理人身份，屬嚴重阻礙清場。另外，黃浩銘則不斷挑戰禁制令內容，並出言嘲諷禁制令申請人一方，陳官認為黃浩銘旨在刺激人群搞對抗，令禁制令申請人一方與佔領人士互相憎恨，阻礙執達主任清場。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：CACV259/17、CACV14/18<br />\n■記者歐陽聯發、楊思雅"},{"pid":"709367dc14c94f27aba84ec9dc2aff25f5529967","tid":534861,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"綠之鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bb40304ec1c700850a44cbf277f100cf6c80cd","tid":534861,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:29:30.000Z","msg":"再搞落去<br />\n有排佢踎🤦🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"f66bc95747ecc0282c43d6328c862f786260bd7d","tid":534861,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放下又座下, 正"},{"pid":"7a70d8acaa6e12b08bb341f39683b2a55e8f429b","tid":534861,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:50:13.000Z","msg":"錢詩文訓醒未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8825c7b72cbcc3e4847d4b011b71cc5dfde2368","tid":534861,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76794d3e94a6f99f1956071441e1846796188665","tid":534861,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:23:24.000Z","msg":"有得出去搵條女出下火都叫唔錯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之蜂加油"},{"pid":"8b6f57b413f18e015c17d32e774fd6ae2bf0037d","tid":534861,"uid":155568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31961d4a69ad7575f19d921bb6deab39b13cef98","tid":534861,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:26:21.000Z","msg":"佢副眼鏡冇次戴得正"},{"pid":"e99fe2101885e808a94d2b68d8254d20ba6036ff","tid":534861,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8825c7b72cbcc3e4847d4b011b71cc5dfde2368","tid":534861,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"坐幾個月點會走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d835d984bfb275eacf733045362cc0ba552f0b0","tid":534861,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"